_header: This world is mutable so sayeth sage
_description: One couplet — for similar content, see 712

OxfBal354.Transcription:
This world is mvtable so seyth sageTherfor gader in tyme or þou
                    fall to age
OxfBal354.Note: In a collection of six proverbial couplets: 6621.7, 5794, 2662, 1433, 835, 3009.
